name: Dureoil LIGHT LUBE Production MTD
query:
select p.name as 'Process Order:Link/Process Order:150',s.name as 'Stock Entry:Link/Stock Entry:150',d.transfer_qty as 'Qty:Float:100',d.valuation_rate as 'Valuation Rate:Float:100',d.amount as 'Amount:Float:100' from `tabStock Entry Detail` d 
left join `tabStock Entry` s on s.name=d.parent
left join `tabProcess Order` p on p.name =s.process_order
where  p.process_type='Waste Oil Re-refining' and s.stock_entry_type='Manufacture' 
and s.docstatus=1 and d.item_code='LLB001'
and YEAR(s.posting_date) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE()) and MONTH(s.posting_date) = MONTH(CURRENT_DATE())
